00:06:45,990 --> 00:06:48,510
and you could kind of have this team of agents

125
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:52,510
or kind of an agent like thing in your CLI

126
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:54,870
and it was working with you in building code.

