00:07:00,890 --> 00:07:02,950
and that particular model was good enough

130
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:05,710
that it could actually start one-shotting apps.

131
00:07:05,710 --> 00:07:09,650
I built this QR code generator just a little bit ago.

