00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:28,110
and Opus 4.5 can one-shot these things quickly.

138
00:07:28,110 --> 00:07:31,190
So this turning point happened,

139
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:32,610
oops, I think I might be frozen.

